Davido ft. Trey Songz – Wetin You Say Davido has finally dropped the date he’ll be releasing his long-awaited album, A Good Time. The ‘Fall’ singer made the news via Instagram on the 28th of October, announcing that his album will be dropping on the 22nd of November 2019. After his last body of work, Son of Mercy, in 2016, Davido has consistently dropped single projects that have not just been hits, they have also pushed him into international scene like Fall and IF, paving the way for big international collaborations like Blow My Mind with American top singer and dancer, Chris Brown.   We'll be having A GOOD TIME on the 22nd of November guys!  #afrobeats #music #Davido #Risky #Notjustok A post shared by  Notjustok.com (@notjustok) on Oct 28, 2019 at 3:02pm PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js   The post Davido Drops Release Date For Upcoming Album, ‘A Good Time’ appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: NotJust okay I remember how elated I was when I received a dm from a friend who worked with Davido’s management team The Plug that I was one of the few people shortlisted for Davido’s listening party. It was like a dream come true. I don’t hide the sentiment I share for… September 6, 2019 In "Music/Video" Davido – A Good Time Overview of Davido – A Good Time (Pre-order) Africa’s most-followed music artiste, Davido triggered a social media frenzy yesterday with the release of his new single “Risky” featuring Popcaan. The hot music single is a follow-up to his Chris Brown-assisted international banger, “Blow My Mind”.… October 25, 2019 In "Music/Video" Akon ft Skales – Control Overview of Akon ft Skales – Control Senegalese-American singer and songwriter, Akon has released his first Afrobeat album and it is tagged ‘Akonda‘. Off the beautiful body of work, we bring you one of the favourites tracks titled “Control“, which is the seventh track. SEE… October 26, 2019 In "Music/Video"